Package utilities

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    Iterator<E>
    This interface will provide an mono-directional iterator for any of the data structures that are specified in this package.
    ListADT<E>
    The ListADT interface is designed to be used as a basis for all the Linear data structures that will be developed in the CPRG 311 class at SAIT.
    QueueADT<E>
    This is the professional Queue Interface for Advanced Object Oriented Programming (CRPG 311) at SAIT Polytechnic.
    StackADT<E>
    This is the professional Stack Interface for Advanced Object Oriented Programming (CRPG 311) at the SAIT Polytechnic.
